By: Hermes
---
That blessed god, the Agathos Daimon, said ‘soul is in body, intellect (νοῦς)
is in soul, and God is in intellect.’ The rarest part of matter then is air;
the rarest part of air is soul; the rarest part of soul is intellect; and the
rarest part of intellect is God.
